data.title: Dive into anything
data.text:
There's places in badi chowdi that do decent paneer, but I always wonder if they use milk powder.

On the costliest side, we have bikanerwala that actually sells fresh paneer per kg, but it's a ridiculous 750rs/kg rate, it's great but that's a lotta money for a kilo!

Any experiences with buying paneer? other than the usual super market heritage/milkymist/amul etc brands
